                            <comment id="17573419" author="skin27" created="Sun, 31 Jul 2022 12:45:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Some additional information:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1) I load everything (routes / routetemplates / routeconfiguration) with the roadLoader.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2) I have camel-xml-io on my classpath&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3) Test parameters creating the route from template&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;in&quot; parameter is &lt;a href=&quot;file:///C:/messages/in?autoCreate=false&amp;amp;directoryMustExist=true&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;file://C:/messages/in&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
