&lt;p&gt;As a sidenote:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The routeConfiguration works when referencing the routeConfiguration from a normal route (not a route template). This however also only works as long as I don&apos;t have camel-xml-jaxb on my classpath (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-17953&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-17953&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately because I need to remove the camel-xml-jaxb the route XML dumper doesn&apos;t work anymore. (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-18305&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-18305&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
